lead_paragraph: The Cleveland Indians took advantage of a controversial bases-loaded wild pitch in their 10-7 victory over the Houston Astros on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Hinch Ejected After 2-Run Wild Pitch, Indians Beat Astros
